      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MESSINA MISS (4) jumped favourite and was too quick with an all-the-way win last start (30.68) at this track in a TG1-4W over 531m. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. In great recent form and expected to measure up again. ALGORITHM (2) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing seven from 12 starts. Finished in the minors latest when third (38.37) at this track and may be close to breaking through. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Bold showing expected. HIJINKERY (6) boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 0.8 lengths (30.58) behind WILMA'S OUR GIRL at Angle Park. Leading player again. BIG STRETCH (3) racing over this distance brings the best out in him.",
